{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>&quot;Music is our past and future.&quot; Dive into a rich tower-defence gacha RPG inspired by music! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/UniqueAndLovableCharacters_Header_NoBG.png?t=1738510929\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/Characters.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>Each character is beautifully designed based on different instruments and genres of music. Enjoy their HD splash art in skill cut-ins, alongside adorable chibi sprites on the battlefield. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/StrategicAndFullOfDepth_Header_NoBG.png?t=1738510929\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/Strategic.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>10 Musical Genres and 7 Virtuoso Archetypes available at launch. Raise and create your own line-up of Virtuosos, and make the intense real-time combat gameplay yours. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/ExcitingAndTowerDefenseGameplay_Header_NoBG.png?t=1738510929\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/TD_Gameplay.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>Test your strategy by deploying Virtuosos to defend against waves of enemies in thrilling tower defense battles. Combine musical abilities and unique archetypes to overcome complex challenges and keep the rhythm alive! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/ComplexWorldbuilding_Header_NoBG.png?t=1738510929\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/Worldbuilding.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>Enter a detailed world that hides many secrets, and experience a visual novel-styled story that takes you through twists and turns. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/HighQualityBGM_Header_NoBG.png?t=1738510929\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/BGM.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>A world based on music, represented by its music. Hear the tracks changing based on your gameplay! </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738510929","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/page.bg.jpg?t=1738510929","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/99075743c3c9aa4552037a1c3b78eabc55df6496/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738510929","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/99075743c3c9aa4552037a1c3b78eabc55df6496/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738510929","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1738510929\" /><br>&quot;Music is our past and future.&quot; Dive into a rich tower-defence gacha RPG inspired by music! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/UniqueAndLovableCharacters_Header_NoBG.png?t=1738510929\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/Characters.gif?t=1738510929\" />